Tiefling

Note

Tieflings are exceptionally rare, and share the same heritage traits as Genasi. This typically means they were born to normal parents under some sort of resonant circumstance that led to the warping of their genetic makeup.

Appearance

Typically born in places where the Resonance is under constant flux, Tieflings are the cursed offspring of normal parents that conceived at the right time to ensure their child would be different. Usually Tiefling births are attributed to magical proximity, such as archmages or wizards that sire children during the height of their magical practices.

Naming Convention

Usually tieflings are named by their parents, or they choose a name if they are cast out.

Biology

Tieflings have colored skin, usually some shade of Red, Purple, or Blue, and hair that is usually black or white. Their heritage doesn't seem to affect their skin tone at birth. Tieflings also have small horns that sprout from their forehead and pointed tails.

Geography

Tieflings are part of society, but are regarded as cursed and the superstitious tend to treat them like bad luck charms. They don't have any cultural center, as they are born into whatever society they came from and whether their parents keep them or cast them out, they don't flock to each other very often.
